            <title>顶盖集成触控板功能，Kidwants 推出 KN1 迷你主机</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/829/169.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/829/169.htm</guid>
